&lt;p&gt;Since 2009 we’ve been making it easy for businesses to take care of their customers and sales opportunities. Capsule is now one of the most popular CRM’s for small businesses and sales teams.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re a UK based company with an office in central Manchester. We’re open to remote working if you’re outside of Manchester, but you need to be in the UK for this position. You’ll be joining a small, dedicated &amp;amp; friendly team that cares deeply about the customer experience. We offer a start-up style culture with a competitive salary and benefits.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;What we’re looking for:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
