  &lt;li&gt;You have excellent communication skills, both written and verbal. You will have a positive style and an ability to describe solutions simply&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;You’re able to read between the lines when necessary to minimise emails back-and-forth - helping customers efficiently is key&lt;/li&gt;
