  &lt;li&gt;You are tech savvy with an interest in web and mobile apps&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Previous experience using help desk software would be a bonus but not essential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;A typical week involves:&lt;/h2&gt;
